file_content.text: You've done it. The bad guys are tripping over each other to get out of King's Pass ASAP.
Nobody's going to make a play here for a long time. You should get back to the spaceport and give Major Brom the good news.
There you are. Let's talk fast. Time's short, and there are eyes everywhere.
Lot of talk about your work. Opposition is thinking of pulling their troops out of King's Pass--thinking maybe we're too well dug in to beat.
Got people with intel on enemy ops. You get with them and shut those ops down, the enemy will think we're far bigger than we are--back off for good.
I'll put a stop to our enemies' plans.
I don't like working with middlemen--give me the details yourself.
Just tell me the plans now.
No good. Too many eyes. Talk to the contacts--they have the details.
